reviewText: Yes. It met and exceeded my expectations in so many ways.

If your child loves the Mario series, this DVD is wonderful. My five year old and my seven year old love Mario everything - movies, plush toys, etc. This DVD is one of many they love to watch - they watch them over and over. This is a good value for Mario fans.
I got this for my nephew and he loved every bit of it. He has watched it over and over.
Kids enjoyed the entire video. Kept them interested thru the entire show and laughed a lot. Will buy more of them
If your child loves Mario, these movies are great. My nine year old loves Mario everything. These movies are an addition to his extensive collection of Mario things. He watches them over and over.
Excellent service and my grandson loves these videos. He was thrilled with this gift.  Would definitely recommend for grandchildren...great gift idea for children.
